For this simulator,it consists of the following parts:
loading part:the initial part of simulator for load an ELF file to the simulator,it takes the name of ELF file and return the text Section's address and load the section should be loaded to the memory
exectuion part:this part run a single instruction of the RISCV codes.This part will starts from the begin of code and run until it meets the syscall stands for EXIT in a loop.
show part:it controls how simulator show itself to the users
